Change in v13:
- Remove a semicolon which bring errors while not building PTP driver.
- Remove few useless EXPORT_SYMBOL().
- Separate PTP consumer symbole which are builtin from PTP provider.

Change in v14:
- Add back missing EXPORT_SYMBOL().
